MonitoringLocationName: North Rim Pipe Discharge to Garden Creek near Pumphouse
MonitoringLocationDescriptionText: The station is at North Rim pipe discharge to Garden Creek near the pumphouse. The site is approximately 420 meters northeast of the Indian Garden Ranger Station. The spring originates on the North Rim, is diverted through a pipe to the South Rim, and serves as the Park's water supply.
